{"tid":644283,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"都係社會的錯，社會的問題","createTime":"2018-04-27T06:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T09:56:40.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c532143be86498ae41d03fdfb4e63fcaee86a2d","tid":644283,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:47:07.000Z","msg":"將問題推在社會的錯，總比人覺得找藉口。<br />\n<br />\n其實大家咁諗，已經被政府洗左腦。<br />\n<br />\n因為社會的錯，社會的問題， 先係你人生真真正正最大的問題和絆真腳石。<br />\n<br />\n簡單論證：<br />\n<br />\n1 你出生在非洲、生在印度、生在中國內地，同你出生在日本、美國、歐洲有幾大分別？<br />\n<br />\n大家都係東亞人，點解蒙古、大陸、台灣、日本會差咁遠？<br />\n<br />\n就算大家都係韓國人，北韓和南韓，差幾遠？<br />\n<br />\n這代表社會制度的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n社會做對，你人生會更美好。<br />\n<br />\n社會的錯，對你人生有極大的影響。<br />\n<br />\n2 講社會科技和政治，你在1850年出世（滿清亂局），1920年出世（民國初期），1960年出世（大陸共產亂局，香港經濟急速起飛），1990年出世（大陸經濟急速起飛，香港經濟停滯不前），你人生會相差極遠？<br />\n<br />\n3 就講大家關注樓價，點解1997年、2003年和2018年會差咁遠？樓價收入比相差咁大？買樓難度相差咁大？此證明社會的錯，令你人生活得更痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n4 比你在滿清年代做皇帝，大富豪，你都冇可能可以嘆冷氣，不可能足不出戶將信息傳送至外國。但你在21世紀，即使做窮撚，甚至乞食，都可以即時與外國通訊。<br />\n<br />\n5 即使最富有的人，都有機會比車撞死。但如果人工智能，智慧自動駕駛技術成熟，過馬路和坐車就會減少99.9%意外。因為社會的科技進步。此證明社會的對，對你人生極重要。"},{"pid":"33da7c316b800ca98cc150ef3379893f44529906","tid":644283,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"可以改變到而自己唔去改變怨社會<br />\n同埋<br />\n真係社會問題係兩樣野黎<br />\n<br />\n不過而家世界資源咁多<br />\n真心要改變既話 點都有方法<br />\n除非你真係生係北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f33411749eea16c9dd4ffa9a524a6b1f921987","tid":644283,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以改變到而自己唔去改變怨社會<br />\n同埋<br />\n真係社會問題係兩樣野黎<br />\n<br />\n不過<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而家世界資源咁多</strong></span><br />\n真心要改變既話 點都有方法<br />\n除非你真係生係北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但全球最富有的100人，<br />\n擁有全球2分1的財富資源喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/politics/the-62-people-who-are-as-wealthy-as-the-poorest-half-of-humanity-combined-a6818766.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-62-people-who-are-as-wealthy-as-the-poorest-half-of-humanity-combined-a6818766.html&d=51wRGTyfgKGB8ujbjWhh8Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=65ffe6d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/politics/the-62-people-who-are-as-wealthy-as-the-poorest-half-of-humanity-combined-a6818766.html</a>"},{"pid":"a18a18269a328f2aa5638d182a5caf2999b4a539","tid":644283,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12f33411749eea16c9dd4ffa9a524a6b1f921987","tid":644283,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以改變到而自己唔去改變怨社會<br />\n同埋<br />\n真係社會問題係兩樣野黎<br />\n<br />\n不過<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而家世界資源咁多</strong></span><br />\n真心要改變既話 點都有方法<br />\n除非你真係生係北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但全球最富有的100人，<br />\n擁有全球2分1的財富資源喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/politics/the-62-people-who-are-as-wealthy-as-the-poorest-half-of-humanity-combined-a6818766.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-62-people-who-are-as-wealthy-as-the-poorest-half-of-humanity-combined-a6818766.html&d=51wRGTyfgKGB8ujbjWhh8Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=65ffe6d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/politics/the-62-people-who-are-as-wealthy-as-the-poorest-half-of-humanity-combined-a6818766.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:26:12.000Z","msg":"準確來講，係但全球最富有的1%人，擁有全球2分1的財富資源。<br />\n<br />\n全球最富的62人總和，相等於全球最窮那35億人的總和。"},{"pid":"8db328146af6d7ba41740aadc00219e7b4dc6fd5","tid":644283,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:48:42.000Z","msg":"原來你講緊錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有能力既點都會係班有錢佬到R到水"},{"pid":"4e695b508365b7f94b1438bd2901079326b6462b","tid":644283,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8db328146af6d7ba41740aadc00219e7b4dc6fd5","tid":644283,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T07:48:42.000Z","msg":"原來你講緊錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有能力既點都會係班有錢佬到R到水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:33:34.000Z","msg":"為何最富的都是美國人？<br />\n為何在香港，早買樓放租俾人可致富，勤力不能致富？<br />\n<br />\n如果全個世界都係超級大賭場，咁真係人人都有機會致富喎。最富的肯定會好有錢。但是個社會一定會係好差。平均的人一定好窮，生活一定差。<br />\n<br />\n社會的錯是係最大的錯。"},{"pid":"8703c528c447687477f89882d64cd9b56f16fd1e","tid":644283,"uid":58852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"改變社會難<br />\n相對上改變自己容易<br />\n用功利主義嘅角度，唔應該哂時間怨社會"},{"pid":"20d75d07cb15c1f76d06d81ddb97784873256a71","tid":644283,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8703c528c447687477f89882d64cd9b56f16fd1e","tid":644283,"uid":58852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"改變社會難<br />\n相對上改變自己容易<br />\n用功利主義嘅角度，唔應該哂時間怨社會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:24:03.000Z","msg":"你呢樣真<br />\n<br />\n以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">功利主義嘅角度</span></strong>，唔應該哂時間埋怨社會及改變社會。<br />\n<br />\n不過其實都係認命，社會的努力，絕對比你的努力重要。<br />\n<br />\n（你點努力都唔會活超過130歲。但社會努力，肯用多些心血在生命科研和物理科研上，可能將來的人，唔駛點努力，都可以輕鬆活到1500歲，有大屋住）"},{"pid":"024e50d10978d0384023a3815912fad66c41207c","tid":644283,"uid":44391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:30:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3197691c8318303ed140cd8ac77390a3c07cc1d","tid":644283,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"024e50d10978d0384023a3815912fad66c41207c","tid":644283,"uid":44391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:30:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:34:19.000Z","msg":"其實人生好多野，都好似你坐緊在架巴士上面，你只係乘客，巴士司機一唔留神，你條命就byebye。你幾健康，幾努力都係假。"},{"pid":"a9789e028e0a0b42b34f82c77fd93b4c3250d47e","tid":644283,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:56:40.000Z","msg":"講到尾我都唔知係講緊問題"}]}